articles.title: Liverpool reach agreement with Brighton and Hove Albion to sign Moisés Caicedo for a British record £110m - The Athletic
articles.description: Liverpool were the highest bidders in an auction held by Brighton for Caicedo, beating Chelsea's bid which was up to £100m.
articles.content:
Liverpool have reached an agreement with Brighton and Hove Albion to sign Moises Caicedo for a British record £110m.
